ard of directors for  years as chair of the finance committee and treasurer from  contributing to aci’s strong financial position he further provided leadership serving on the board’s executive committee from  larry peiros has been a tremendous asset to aci and to the cleaning products industry atlarge said ernie rosenberg aci president  ceo those of us on the staff who have worked with him directly have deep respect and affection a mere recitation of the positions he’s held does not capture how much of a contribution he has made and how important his leadership has been to the development of the institute and its staff i am personally deeply grateful that i had the opportunity to work with and learn from larry rosenberg added for decades aci has been at the forefront of promoting the benefits of cleaning products and protecting the ability of its members to formulate products that best meet consumer needs said larry peiros it has been exciting and personally fulfilling to be a part of this effort working with respected leaders from other member companies as well as a group of extremely capable professionals that make up the aci staff aci’s distinguished service award is named in honor of the late elva walker spillane the former national purity llc chief executive who served on the association’s board for  years the award honors an individual for extensive or exceptional service to aci who promoted the growth and interests of the institute and the industries it represents and who exercised outstanding leadership within the institute  the american cleaning institute® aci is the home of the us cleaning products industry® and represents the  billion us cleaning products market aci members include the formulators of soaps detergents and general cleaning products used in household commercial industrial and institutional settings companies that supply ingredients and finished packaging for these products and oleochemical producers aci wwwcleaninginstituteorg and its members are dedicated to improving health and the quality of life through sustainable cleaning products and practices  back to news       contact aci become a member members only photo galleries videos      american cleaning institute   all rights reserved   washington dc   site map  terms  conditions  privacy policy